column5: I was wondering how many here will make the trip across the boarder to save some money for the big turkeyday sales that go on in the USA this thursday. What sotres do you like?  I usualy hit Meijer or Wal-mart depending on the flyers sometimes you can save alot of money how about you what are your plans?
Hey Mike, buy something nice for me! Like a case of beer!    I'll gladly pay you for it!
Hey paul is a case for you like 6 keges tied together?
They don't have beer down there.
